cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper deals with the problem of utilizing multiple sets of images to improve the accuracy of controlling the steering angle in autonomous vehicles. This involves computer vision (CV) techniques for image processing, robotics (RO) for autonomous vehicle control, machine learning (LG) for deep learning techniques, artificial intelligence (AI) for end-to-end solutions, and systems and control (SY) for the overall system design. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.SY, in that order.
